title: #92Noon with Michael Russo!
description: The Athletic's, Michael Russo, is in for PA today. He is joined by FSN's, Anthony LaPanta to discuss the comeback the Wild is experiencing. Jonny Athletic in studio to discuss the Wolves and the Vikings. Athletic National Editor, Craig Custance, joins over the phone. And finally, former Viking, Chad Greenway, who now prides himself as Head of Wayzata Girls Basketball, among other things, answers your questions.
